## Creating a student

POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName":"<script>Shino</script>",
    "lastName":"Aburame",
    "email":"SHIno@GMAIL.COM",
    "age":9,
    "role":"student",
    "password":"Naruto0511"
}

### Signin a student

POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/signin
